messages.title: SORRY we missed you
messages.content: The General Election takes place on Thursday, May 7... and it’s an important one for Scotland. We must elect a strong team that will put the people of Scotland first. Dr Lisa Cameron, is committed to winning that strong voice for Scotland in Westminster. This constituency will be at the heart of everything she does. Elect a politician who cares.

images.caption: Dr Lisa Cameron, your SNP Candidate

leaflet.additionalNotes: Promoted by Ian McAllan, SNP, Strathmore House, East Kilbride G74 1LF on behalf of Dr Lisa Cameron, SNP. Printed by Forward Pixels, Kelvin Industrial Estate, East Kilbride G75 0YL
